ictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/riico-grants-approval-for-rfc-to-sell-industrial-properties-in-rajasthan/130202734?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-189645/130202734.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}]}